                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-220-defend1311 t18340703-220-deflabel1227"></join> for about a fortnight - we missed three spoons, one at a time - part of one was found at a refiner's, and one on the prisoner.</p>
